column1: TH - New solution for ANC prefill
column26:
Find the new solution for ANC prefill to solve the below issue:
https://woodpecker.atlassian.net/browse/SGP-4708

Enclosed you will find a list of make and model, sorted by its popularity (measured by clickout)

1. The engine capacity is not provided since we don't have the data
Therefore, for those car models that have more than 1 engine capacity , the sequence of the prefill can be from low to high engine capacity

For example

HONDA CIVIC, we have 5 engine capacity which are 1500, 1700, 1800 and 2000

The sequence of the prefill can be 1500, then 1700, then 1800 and then 2000.

2. Other car make or model that are not included in the attached list, can be considered as a not popular make / model. We dont need to prefill them.



Scope - This improvement will be applied for whole site. All suppliers.
Documentation - Detailed technical solution will be documented here: https://woodpecker.atlassian.net/wiki/display/TD/New+solution+to+improve+ANC+prefill
